My teeth have not been in a good condition (with 10 existing implants and several root canals prior to that) and I have visited several dentists in many cities in India, wherever I was posted. 
This is the first time I have seen a doctor, call in two more of his experts in related areas, and they  had a full and  open discussion on the various treatment possibilities – pros and cons for many options. 
I have not seen such a candid discussion anywhere else: I think it’s a sign of very high competence; they knew their stuff, able to visualise exactly how the treatment would progress. 
And after a few tests, they had another round of discussions. 
I have come back with a lot of faith in all the three doctors I met with Dr. Anil Soni, Dr. Tyagi and Dr. Salil Kochar. 
You will not go wrong if you decide to get your dental work done by visiting this clinic; very open to accept your suggestions. 
Thanks, 
Ajay Anand
